            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This assert and reliance on absolute position in linebuf was necessary before extending the `fill_foldcolumn()` loop to draw filler `' '`'s instead of calling `draw_coll_fill()`. Could have gotten rid of it after refactoring that, I can make another PR.",
